fields.calculatedFormula:
if(
    ISPICKVAL(hed__Primary_Address_Type__c,"Work"),
    if(ISBLANK(MailingStreet) , "" , MailingStreet & ", ") &
    if(ISBLANK(MailingCity) , "" , MailingCity & ", ") &
    if(ISBLANK(MailingState) , "" , MailingState & " ") &
    if(ISBLANK(MailingPostalCode) , "" , MailingPostalCode) &
    If(ISBLANK(MailingCountry ) , "" , ", " & MailingCountry)
    ,
    if(ISPICKVAL(hed__Secondary_Address_Type__c,"Work"),
    if(ISBLANK(OtherStreet) , "" , OtherStreet & ", ") &
    if(ISBLANK(OtherCity) , "" , OtherCity & ", ") &
    if(ISBLANK(OtherState) , "" , OtherState & " ") &
    if(ISBLANK(OtherPostalCode) , "" , OtherPostalCode) &
    If(ISBLANK(OtherCountry ) , "" , ", " & OtherCountry)
    ,
    "")
)
fields.inlineHelpText: If you've set "Work" as the Primary Address type, the Work Address is populated with the Mailing Address values. If "Work" is the Secondary Address type, the Work Address is populated with the "Other Address" values. This field is read-only.
fields.label: Work Address
fields.name: hed__Work_Address__c

fields.inlineHelpText: When selected, this Contact's address won't be synced with the Household Default or Seasonal Address. Use this to maintain a separate Mailing Address for this particular Contact. (Applies to Household Contacts only.)
